{"tid":166944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖)要考DSE通識既入黎","createTime":"2017-03-22T13:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T15:53:28.000Z","uid":92736,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0cff39d3f7a31ac77c58a21f12356b3d3adf1731","tid":166944,"uid":92736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:25:54.000Z","msg":"細佬係今年DSE自修生，重考英文、中史、通識<br />\n其實通識唔係考得差，有5，只係我覺得我點都唔止呢個分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （英文就不要說了）<br />\n然而發現公屋冇錢自修生真係幾仆街，冇錢補習又冇學反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但通識個模式同重點議題又年年變⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n所以小弟今日係到share幾個學通識既免費平台，希望一眾有能力既窮撚都可以唔落後於班私補撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （可能好多巴打已經知呢兩舊野，我只係想share下比d冇留意既同學知，唔好屌我講廢話，當年我學校d老師真係提都冇提過有呢d野，我係自修先知）<br />\n<br />\n第一個係Yahoo! 新聞app入面個通識平台，d內容都幾全面（建議用手機版，ipad個版面好亂）<br />\n<br />\n有免費既補習名師筆記(即係補習社果d)：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Q2j2p4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Q2j2p4.png&h=61cc785b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0604Fy2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0604Fy2.png&h=a0bf9273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有各類答題框架：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ph23006.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fph23006.png&h=da469b26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有tip熱門議題:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wY5Qi97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwY5Qi97.png&h=3c4cd87d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家去app store 或play store search 雅虎新聞入面就有（記得係app入面關左個通知佢，唔係佢會日日提你睇新聞）<br />\n<br />\n第二個就可能好多人都知，就係香港電台個通識網：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91B3C8s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91B3C8s.png&h=58277ff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有概念既分析：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xmALEm1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxmALEm1.png&h=538622d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一d幾得意既通識漫畫：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8C3uHy5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8C3uHy5.png&h=40696ea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港台個網相對上就冇咁考試導向，始終佢地係「學習」為本。<br />\nYahoo! 果個冇咁有趣，不過比較應試導向<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYahoo! 新聞通識：（建議用手機版，ipad個版面好亂）<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.yahoo.infohub\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.yahoo.infohub&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=3f0fcd5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.yahoo.infohub</a><br />\nApple：<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/yahoo%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E/id425655609?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fyahoo%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%2584%25A6%25E9%25BB%259E%2Fid425655609%3Fmt%3D8&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=554b7d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/yahoo%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E/id425655609?mt=8</a><br />\n港台通識網：<a href=\"http://www.liberalstudies.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.liberalstudies.hk%2F&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=16ffd36a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.liberalstudies.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n希望學校老師廢同冇錢補習既同學唔好鬥氣唔讀某d科<br />\n你肯搵依家個世界好多免費資源比你到<br />\n<br />\n大家加油啦！<br />\n反應好會share埋其他科既學習資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8cb59021191e0faa7ceec2d2508bec9a44e0f5","tid":166944,"uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:27:25.000Z","msg":"唔錯喎又<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：已上岸，當年5星，不過幫你推一推啦"},{"pid":"6e3f49328b95e1c02c11e369ea54684606ba4b9a","tid":166944,"uid":92736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:28:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔錯喎又<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：已上岸，當年5星，不過幫你推一推啦</blockquote><br />\nthanks bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我覺得幾好就係apps方便搭車行路睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b5a7796d595c957e57a51592cfe68d92844972","tid":166944,"uid":77880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:31:04.000Z","msg":"最d share 就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家等死"},{"pid":"bd88938d5f64a3851a327d974646359747a30eb7","tid":166944,"uid":77880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最d share 就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家等死</blockquote><br />\n早"},{"pid":"0f0f7d03166fadd74edd06b01340ba641fa6e1b2","tid":166944,"uid":92743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中大仔表示今年<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">個補習學生</span>重考<br />\n推比佢睇下"},{"pid":"2002845f6b8128b338542a676e84ac7207ee21fe","tid":166944,"uid":92736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最d share 就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家等死</blockquote><br />\n早</blockquote><br />\n巴打唔好放棄，幾日時間可以差一個grade架<br />\n有時唔係話學新野<br />\n係喚醒一d已有知識，令自己有最好狀態去考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油"},{"pid":"356bac8bb3f7cd0db2fbc3edc5180ce457ac70b9","tid":166944,"uid":77880,"like":0,"dis