quote>多謝巴打<br />\nbookmark左</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2243e897533655b2a011fb93d8e95f3951115d5e","tid":166944,"uid":65885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T17:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幫推 大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係上年嘅考生 窮撚冇補過習5**咗<br />\n我得 大家都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打可唔可以講下點做到，好勁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 個人覺得拆題同留意keywords好緊要 <br />\n做個陣千祈唔好急 要睇清題目 諗好point先開波做<br />\n好似講緊廢話咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真講日常準備就冇乜 因為文科人 手字就好快<br />\n平時本身都有留意開新聞 我覺得可以睇緊個陣自己思考多啲<br />\n唔好死記硬背 係冇用的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df36c685f28ea895f1ae7e499b3f5c8aa219773","tid":166944,"uid":17250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T18:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>教多一個俾巴打<br />\n小卒資源區有雅集既question bank<br />\n有大量議題同point 背<br />\n睇熟後根據佢既point寫個百搭point for 諗唔到時候用<br />\n再加上答題技巧<br />\n通識就變成呃分入大學既科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年我都係最後兩星期先溫，不過當然有底<br />\n利申，2014 通識五星，三大，可惜始終唔夠其他人英文五星有用，通識只係幫我入大學，以脫貧為目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝巴打分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英文當然重要，但要好耐時間浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但通識短時間改變到好多野</blockquote><br />\n我係絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e79518ebb2d409b21bb048d02970e95c39fb44b","tid":166944,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>教多一個俾巴打<br />\n小卒資源區有雅集既question bank<br />\n有大量議題同point 背<br />\n睇熟後根據佢既point寫個百搭point for 諗唔到時候用<br />\n再加上答題技巧<br />\n通識就變成呃分入大學既科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年我都係最後兩星期先溫，不過當然有底<br />\n利申，2014 通識五星，三大，可惜始終唔夠其他人英文五星有用，通識只係幫我入大學，以脫貧為目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝巴打分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英文當然重要，但要好耐時間浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但通識短時間改變到好多野</blockquote><br />\n我係絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲咪臭閪爭撚住認絲打 <br />\n我屌你老母啊"},{"pid":"f3e39e6437c0a12ad902b1af8775a0cec0c0d397","tid":166944,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一件事 寫字寫靚啲 改卷用2分鐘 自己稔</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手字其實係咪真係有得練</blockquote><br />\n認真有得練 自己之前練過下硬筆字楷書 雖然唔係好耐但都擺脫咗小學雞字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似話啲字睇唔清有機會變senior marker改，唔知真得假</blockquote><br />\n睇唔清點解要比senior marker 改?<br />\n點解要幫你撚成篇文<br />\n<br />\n以前讀中學個陣同幾玩得埋既英文啊sir吹水個陣<br />\n佢語重心長咁講 記得寫字寫靚啲<br />\n佢改文幾蚊至十蚊一分 總知唔多<br />\n佢話佢改好簡單<br />\n- first impression 你啲字靚唔靚<br />\n- 字數適量<br />\n- 淨睇topic sentences <br />\n- evidence elaborate 個啲臘一臘眼 <br />\n- 睇intro conclu<br />\n之後就比分 真係成段同你慢慢撚 我改多啲唔好?<br />\n比得高定低分 關佢撚事"},{"pid":"f1458d121a926d6a2112c3be70a9e410704bf678","tid":166944,"uid":92736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T15:00:50.000Z","msg":"就考推反上去先"},{"pid":"34af79ad83b413117f0181dfe382927df4eee43c","tid":166944,"uid":92736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":